Hi guys:),

Can anyone tell me what mods were used inEve Sample Return ?

Ty.

The green tank in the first picture is from the Kethane mod and the fairing on launch is Procedural Fairings. Not sure about the balloons on ascent from Eve (because I haven't used them) but try Hooligan Labs.
Some of the engines come from KW Rocketry.
that one engine at the very bottom is KSPX
I can see lights from B9 Aerospace
